{"tid":2441031,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"二十年前既數碼暴龍卡。","createTime":"2021-03-10T11:26:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T14:31:34.000Z","uid":263448,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"63d7e51047a3a97b808b49a725e428258d955102","tid":2441031,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"執屋時搵到小學雞時代買既數碼卡。<br />\n應該就正版黎，當年老翻冇咁好品質。<br />\n香港唔係日本，當年資訊又唔發達，無可能知自己差邊張，又搵唔到同好換，甚至連玩都唔識，所以唔齊。<br />\n求期影一小部份，就一張閃卡同幾張金字。<br />\n唔知值唔值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202103/36ada033186594564723ddece1cb7ded.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202103%2F36ada033186594564723ddece1cb7ded.JPG&h=d1cdd518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202103/1c83dd3c43323eed468ff710b9018ee7.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202103%2F1c83dd3c43323eed468ff710b9018ee7.JPG&h=ff8ef317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202103/d32bce1af1ad601e4c443dc58095b184.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202103%2Fd32bce1af1ad601e4c443dc58095b184.JPG&h=7acc247f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202103/878af448794304c8c963ec5a15c0b0a0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202103%2F878af448794304c8c963ec5a15c0b0a0.JPG&h=5aabd9ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9844241363b82ef5506aab1dbdbe83e7970e8a8","tid":2441031,"uid":60434,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T11:27:31.000Z","msg":"廢紙依家幾錢一kg"},{"pid":"7585724a155cfd2c43fd5bbe32462c8f57d6896e","tid":2441031,"uid":156936,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T11:29:03.000Z","msg":"之前岩岩播完套劇場版個陣好多人收<br />\n問題係你啲卡廢"},{"pid":"a84